Text: Du råkar inte ha alla sju i serien?!?!? Det skulle ju vara helt underbart ;o)

Thanks for uploading this movie! I've just started learning Swedish, but I'm already collecting DVDs in Swedish with Swe subs for practising the language (later). On the basis of my experience movies like that are not easy to find. If you know about other movies with Swedish audio + subs (+ Eng subs even better, preferebly in the romance category, which is the simplest to understand) please let me know here or at ksoktogon@yahoo.com. Thanks in advance!!!
